This is my interpretation:
###
The white dragon represents the positive, good, and holy.\nThe red dragon represents the negative, bad, and unholy.\nThe computer manufacturing genious represents the negative, bad, and unholy.\nThe computer system represents the negative, bad, and unholy.\nNo password represents no rules.\nThe red dragon got stuck in the system because he really liked it there.\nThe white dragon destroyed all the computers in some massive destruction.

